!!! update the README -- the only documentation we have.

Signal handler for '-P' to catch/ignore SIG_INT

-M -- mmap() so as to avoid sharing of anon vmas.  [not so easy].
	work in progress as of 27jan2010
	maybe not needed with RvR's private anon_vma patches.  TEST!

Option [-A?] to bind tests to all cpus in a node before moving on to next node.
Currently, cpuids are interleaved over nodes on [HP] x86_64 platforms where
pft has been tested.

